com.google.api.gbase.client
Class ItemTypeDescription

java.lang.Object
  com.google.api.gbase.client.ItemTypeDescription

public class ItemTypeDescription
extends java.lang.Object

A description of an item type done by the gm: tags in a google base entry. Make sure the current feed is an item type feed and then get the ItemTypeDescription for the entry using: GoogleBaseEntry.getGoogleBaseMetadata().getItemTypeDescription()
